Text: and Happy Holidays to all of my Big Braves and Little Guides and Princesses This is just a reminder on the Childrens Museum activity planned for Saturday This activity will be from Noon until pm The admission is for the Parent and the Child Please keep in mind that the trip does not necessarily have to begin at Noon This is an activity where you can set an arrival time that is convenient for yourself or your tribe Just remember that the Museum closes at pm Unfortunately I have an emergency that can not be avoided so I will be arriving probably later in the day if at all Please contact anyone who you feel may benefit from this outing whether it be tribal members or family and friends I will be in touch again soon to give details on the Holiday Skating Party at the Sharpstown skating center I hear that Santa is going to be there so Im sure that its going to be a blast Howling Wolf
